item.title: Project 1 - Seattle Crime
item.description: This notebook is an in-depth analysis of Seattle Police Department (SPD) Crimes Data downloaded from Seattle Open Data on June 30th 2021. Above plot shows that crime rates in Seattle decreased in the year 2011-2012, then steadily increases starting in 2013, with the highest rate in 2020.
